race.comment: CRICKLE OWL VIC (7) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 2 length win at this track in a handy 19.98. Draws out wide but goes well over this trip. The one to beat again. BACALAR (1) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 4 lengths at this track. One of main contenders. MORRISETTE (2) has hit the frame here at the last two runs, most recently finishing second beaten a nose (20.26). Well placed and gets his chance. MONKEY PANTS (3) scored last time and can measure up again.
